    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat, and a few small dings on the passenger side panels. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, it starts and runs, but it would benefit from a thorough inspection and some upcoming maintenance to ensure continued reliability. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable, high-utility vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
