    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has several visible scuffs and some paint fading, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and a few non-essential electronic quirks. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance needs.",
      "price": 20000.0,
